    citation-twoiaf-aenys-i:
        source: source-twoiaf
        properties:
            locator: "The Targaryen Kings: Aenys I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Reign of Aenys I: rebellions (Harren the Red, Vulture King, Lodos the Second), marriage of Rhaena and Aegon, conflict with the Faith, exile of Maegor, death in 42 AC. Character portrait of the indecisive king."
